
= Italian organisation which aims to legalize p2p of copyrighted contents through global licenses


URL = http://www.scambioetico.org/

=Description=

Paolo Brini:

"ScambioEtico was born 4 years ago with the aim to legalize p2p of
copyrighted contents through global licenses, with a model already
suggested by Electronic Frontier Foundation and properly adapted to
italian reality. During the years, some secondary objectives has been
added, such as to reach an "armistice" on the war against p2p.
  
Nowadays, it appears clear that p2p of copyrighted contents is a
peculiar problem on the wider background of citizens digital rights.
(http://www.scambioetico.org/index.php?topic=351.0)



